  "title" : "Getting random numbers in Java",
  "body" : "<p>I would like to get a random value between 1 to 50 in Java.</p>\n\n<p>How may I do that with the help of <code>Math.random();</code>?</p>\n\n<p>How do I bound the values that <code>Math.random()</code> returns?</p>\n"
